text.tspan: WITH THE ENGINE RUNNING AT AROUND
VOLTAGE AT THE BATTERY. THE BATTERY
STOP THE ENGINE AND DISCONNECT THE
WIRES IN TURN. THE OUTPUT VOLTAGE MUST
EXCEED 15 VOLTS AC FROM EACH WIRE.
RAISE THE ENGINE SPEED ABOVE 4,000 RPM.
WIRES IN TURN. THE OUTPUT VOLTAGE MUST
NOW EXCEED 30 VOLTS AC FROM EACH WIRE.
ENSURE THE BATTERY IS IN GOOD
